definition: entity/substance/thing that has a material existence (as opposed to a conceptual, virtual or online existence)/the real thing (as opposed to an image or model of it)
brick and mortar business/physical (rather than online) retail store

sentences.chinese: 實體基礎設施和能源行業。

sentences.english: Q. Is the house the Cullens live in real?
sentences.chinese: 卡倫一家住的房子是有實體的嗎？

sentences.english: Unlike a changeset, a shelveset is a non-versioned entity.
sentences.chinese: 與變更集不同的是，擱置集是沒有建立版本的實體。

sentences.english: This ensures that I have the right business entity.
sentences.chinese: 這就確保了我得到了正確的業務實體。

sentences.english: MFN clause generally applies to the substantive problem.
sentences.chinese: 最惠國待遇條款一般適用於實體問題。

sentences.english: Eachagent has an Area Mask which describes which areas it can usewhen navigating.
sentences.chinese: 區域遮罩用於某區域的路徑只能通過某種尋路實體。

sentences.english: The solid mineralizing model for a underground gold mine is researched on the basis of orebody block as a unit.
sentences.chinese: 以礦塊爲單位，研究某地下金礦的實體礦化模型。

sentences.english: At the same time, the engineering department made shells of the solid models.
sentences.chinese: 同時，工程部門製作實體模型的外殼。

sentences.english: In the world of international marketing, governments, quasi- government agencies, and profit-seeking and nonprofit entities are frequently buyers.
sentences.chinese: 以及贏利與非贏利實體都經常充當買家的角色。

sentences.english: The physical layouts of classrooms vary. Initially, student desks stand in rows.
sentences.chinese: 課堂裏的實體佈局變化，首先是，課桌排成行。

sentences.english: Create a new order by posting an XML entity to a service.
sentences.chinese: 通過向服務發送一個XML實體來創建一個新訂單。

sentences.english: Neuroblastoma is the most common extracranial solid tumor in children.
sentences.chinese: 神經母細胞瘤是兒童最常見的顱外實體腫瘤。

sentences.english: The interface uses the schema describing the entity record and any other parameters.
sentences.chinese: 該接口使用了描述實體記錄的模式和任何其他的參數。

sentences.english: This establishes entity correspondence between data that is physically distributed.
sentences.chinese: 數據之間的實體通信在物理上是分佈式的。

sentences.english: He also describes innumerous situations when he was helped by nonphysical entities.
sentences.chinese: 他也描述了無數次得到非肉身實體幫助的情形。

sentences.english: There are several entities described in the AMQ specification.
sentences.chinese: 在AMQ規範中描述了一些實體。
